{"2962470": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "貝爾蘭德的侵蝕-姬騎士莉絲緹亞", "steam_appid": 2962470, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事簡介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/3821fc362c49acd8fd39f35452db3906.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莉絲緹亞，曾經的地方貴族小姐與騎士長，因為得罪領主被迫逃亡到了國境的邊陲，充斥著魔物與強盜的前線貝爾蘭德。莉絲緹亞成為了公會冒險者開始接受委託，卻又被設計中了淫慾詛咒。不僅失去了強大的魔力，還獲得了一個不斷渴望性愛的身體。為了籌出治療淫慾詛咒的費用，莉絲緹亞不得不從最弱小的冒險者重新做起，帶著日漸高漲的性慾，在這個危機四伏的前線地帶工作賺錢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/25a80b1994208da0f75d86584f9921a6.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/25a80b1994208da0f75d86584f9921a6.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/25a80b1994208da0f75d86584f9921a6.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d830c4234143ee92703391909c005bad.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d830c4234143ee92703391909c005bad.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d830c4234143ee92703391909c005bad.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲內容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制RPG。玩家要扮演落難的姬騎士莉絲緹亞，以新人冒險家的身分，探索豐富的地圖，在危險的貝爾蘭德接取村民委託。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著任務的進行，玩家必須學習更強大的技能，蒐集素材升級自己的武器。在面對無法輕易取勝的敵人時，透過不同的技能組合，找到敵人的弱點進行反制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/88d292926217e9f3730788e63a07c0f1.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/88d292926217e9f3730788e63a07c0f1.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/88d292926217e9f3730788e63a07c0f1.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天時，玩家要在冒險者旅店透過任務委託、打工、擊敗魔物等方式，提升自身等級與收入。進入夜晚野外會出現危險的異變生物，可以使用火把驅趕黑暗中的怪物避開戰鬥，在黑夜裡繼續探索。  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/22036ecfeee172aacc40909a7bddd79e.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/22036ecfeee172aacc40909a7bddd79e.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/22036ecfeee172aacc40909a7bddd79e.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆充滿危險的貝爾蘭德</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史萊姆：</strong>隨處可見的史萊姆。號稱最弱的魔物。但在不同環境會衍伸出不同的亞種。有些充滿危險性，一不小心就會失足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/2877d40191cc62c2e3c977ed1675a6c9.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>走路菇：</strong>長腳的魔化香菇。一旦遇到身經百戰的個體，或者變異的個體，就要特別小心了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d2fbe171291c63414ade1878b7e9c1ea.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小混混：</strong>盤踞在貝爾蘭德近郊的飢渴強盜們。在戰鬥中會不擇手段。他們最喜歡一個人在外面行走的女性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/cb4a0ec473fd4830e58bd14948cc8c77.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>哥布林：</strong>弱小的人形魔物。但不能因為他們體型小就小看他們。當哥布林中有領袖出現，一群各司其職的哥布林，就跟一支軍隊一樣恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/fe2d984e43f7821bd1318fe12428b8c1.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多強大的菁英敵人…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/9ef067969f7bb4a3a2e7db3bd068f25f.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●以凌辱、異種姦為主，50張的動態HCG與立繪差分。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●獨特的暗黑世界觀：</strong>融合動漫與寫實的暗黑奇幻美術風格，帶來了獨特肉體色氣感，與被玷汙的視覺衝擊。除了主角之外，每一隻怪物、NPC的CG與點陣圖也都是全新繪製，非使用RPG Maker的泛用素材，創造出更符合這個世界觀的視覺體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※為了符合遊戲世界觀，本遊戲中有許多強暴、強迫事件，也沒有處女通關路線。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/185771d6406431e6fe37eb45606ee596.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/185771d6406431e6fe37eb45606ee596.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/185771d6406431e6fe37eb45606ee596.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/736df811efa5cfd270bebadfa4936266.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/736df811efa5cfd270bebadfa4936266.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/736df811efa5cfd270bebadfa4936266.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●多元的技能系統：</strong>刺擊、斬擊、重擊三大系統的劍技，能交叉運用出破甲、出血等特殊攻擊效果。也有消耗性慾值來發動的性技，讓戰鬥過程更加豐富多變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/3044f0058a9a49dc8552553d8cb1f976.avif?t=1776220614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras_big/3044f0058a9a49dc8552553d8cb1f976.webp?t=1776220614 width=1560 height=873 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●晝夜系統：</strong>當進入夜晚時，野外會出現高危險的異變生物，同時視野也會變暗，增加不小心遭遇敵人的機會。玩家可以使用火炬、提燈等道具來點亮周圍的環境，同時驅趕黑暗中的怪物來避開戰鬥。因此在夜晚時，玩家必需要使用與白天不同的探索方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/f2fac5c991ea8a0bce141437980b0be7.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/f2fac5c991ea8a0bce141437980b0be7.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/f2fac5c991ea8a0bce141437980b0be7.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事簡介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/3821fc362c49acd8fd39f35452db3906.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莉絲緹亞，曾經的地方貴族小姐與騎士長，因為得罪領主被迫逃亡到了國境的邊陲，充斥著魔物與強盜的前線貝爾蘭德。莉絲緹亞成為了公會冒險者開始接受委託，卻又被設計中了淫慾詛咒。不僅失去了強大的魔力，還獲得了一個不斷渴望性愛的身體。為了籌出治療淫慾詛咒的費用，莉絲緹亞不得不從最弱小的冒險者重新做起，帶著日漸高漲的性慾，在這個危機四伏的前線地帶工作賺錢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/25a80b1994208da0f75d86584f9921a6.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/25a80b1994208da0f75d86584f9921a6.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/25a80b1994208da0f75d86584f9921a6.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d830c4234143ee92703391909c005bad.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d830c4234143ee92703391909c005bad.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d830c4234143ee92703391909c005bad.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲內容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制RPG。玩家要扮演落難的姬騎士莉絲緹亞，以新人冒險家的身分，探索豐富的地圖，在危險的貝爾蘭德接取村民委託。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著任務的進行，玩家必須學習更強大的技能，蒐集素材升級自己的武器。在面對無法輕易取勝的敵人時，透過不同的技能組合，找到敵人的弱點進行反制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/88d292926217e9f3730788e63a07c0f1.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/88d292926217e9f3730788e63a07c0f1.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/88d292926217e9f3730788e63a07c0f1.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天時，玩家要在冒險者旅店透過任務委託、打工、擊敗魔物等方式，提升自身等級與收入。進入夜晚野外會出現危險的異變生物，可以使用火把驅趕黑暗中的怪物避開戰鬥，在黑夜裡繼續探索。  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/22036ecfeee172aacc40909a7bddd79e.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/22036ecfeee172aacc40909a7bddd79e.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/22036ecfeee172aacc40909a7bddd79e.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆充滿危險的貝爾蘭德</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史萊姆：</strong>隨處可見的史萊姆。號稱最弱的魔物。但在不同環境會衍伸出不同的亞種。有些充滿危險性，一不小心就會失足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/2877d40191cc62c2e3c977ed1675a6c9.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>走路菇：</strong>長腳的魔化香菇。一旦遇到身經百戰的個體，或者變異的個體，就要特別小心了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/d2fbe171291c63414ade1878b7e9c1ea.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小混混：</strong>盤踞在貝爾蘭德近郊的飢渴強盜們。在戰鬥中會不擇手段。他們最喜歡一個人在外面行走的女性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/cb4a0ec473fd4830e58bd14948cc8c77.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>哥布林：</strong>弱小的人形魔物。但不能因為他們體型小就小看他們。當哥布林中有領袖出現，一群各司其職的哥布林，就跟一支軍隊一樣恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/fe2d984e43f7821bd1318fe12428b8c1.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多強大的菁英敵人…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/9ef067969f7bb4a3a2e7db3bd068f25f.avif?t=1776220614\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●以凌辱、異種姦為主，50張的動態HCG與立繪差分。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●獨特的暗黑世界觀：</strong>融合動漫與寫實的暗黑奇幻美術風格，帶來了獨特肉體色氣感，與被玷汙的視覺衝擊。除了主角之外，每一隻怪物、NPC的CG與點陣圖也都是全新繪製，非使用RPG Maker的泛用素材，創造出更符合這個世界觀的視覺體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※為了符合遊戲世界觀，本遊戲中有許多強暴、強迫事件，也沒有處女通關路線。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/185771d6406431e6fe37eb45606ee596.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/185771d6406431e6fe37eb45606ee596.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/185771d6406431e6fe37eb45606ee596.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/736df811efa5cfd270bebadfa4936266.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/736df811efa5cfd270bebadfa4936266.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/736df811efa5cfd270bebadfa4936266.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●多元的技能系統：</strong>刺擊、斬擊、重擊三大系統的劍技，能交叉運用出破甲、出血等特殊攻擊效果。也有消耗性慾值來發動的性技，讓戰鬥過程更加豐富多變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/3044f0058a9a49dc8552553d8cb1f976.avif?t=1776220614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras_big/3044f0058a9a49dc8552553d8cb1f976.webp?t=1776220614 width=1560 height=873 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●晝夜系統：</strong>當進入夜晚時，野外會出現高危險的異變生物，同時視野也會變暗，增加不小心遭遇敵人的機會。玩家可以使用火炬、提燈等道具來點亮周圍的環境，同時驅趕黑暗中的怪物來避開戰鬥。因此在夜晚時，玩家必需要使用與白天不同的探索方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/f2fac5c991ea8a0bce141437980b0be7.poster.avif?t=1776220614\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/f2fac5c991ea8a0bce141437980b0be7.webm?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/extras/f2fac5c991ea8a0bce141437980b0be7.mp4?t=1776220614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "暗黑奇幻風格RPG。落難的姬騎士莉絲緹亞，被設計中了淫慾詛咒，失去了強大的魔力。他要以新人冒險家的身分重新出發，用一個不斷渴望性愛的身體，在充滿各種不懷好意敵人、怪物的貝爾蘭德冒險，試圖再一次成為被倚重的騎士。", "supported_languages": "繁體中文, 英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文, 簡體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/25e80c812ef2ff94eea3366c3e4959e8fed3fb97/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776220614", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/834ba1510e6fb550ceb9be202949acb81d4f5882/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776220614", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962470/834ba1510e6fb550ceb9be202949acb81d4f5882/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776220614", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "All characters are above 18.", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026 第 4 季"}}}}